profile:
Welcome to Viktoria Professional Movers – a company where customer care and satisfaction are our top priorities. 
 
There's no doubt about it, moving can be stressful!   Choosing responsible and experienced movers is one of the ways to alleviate that stress. When choosing a moving & storage company price is important, however the level of service your moving company provides you with is even more important, and often times cheap moving companies can end up costing you a fortune! Unfortunately, our industry abounds with companies whose aim to book as many jobs as they can by whatever means necessary. Many "lowball" estimates quickly balloon with unexpected charges while hurried workers provide disappointing service. For many of these companies protecting your property and ensuring your satisfaction is last on their list of priorities.
 
At Viktoria Professional Movers it's not about the number of moves, it's about the number of customers we leave happy & satisfied. Moving doesn't have to be complicated. Let us walk you through the process and get you on the way to a stress-free move to your new home. The key to a successful move is organization and we are the experts.
 
Whether you require moving, packing, or self-storage, you will never be just another client to us. Ever.
 
PIANO MOVING | PACKING MATERIALS | PACKING SERVICES, MOVING BIN RENTAL | STORAGE | SELF-STORAGE | LONG-DISTANCE MOVES | MOVING SUPPLIES

profile:
Kleiner Moving & Storage are locally owned and operated moving and storage company who strive to give clients a stress-free experience. Every project is different and we work towards a customized solution for each individual or family or company. Sit down, relax, and let our movers do the heavy lifting. With our all-in-one pricing and services, our goal is to help you make a smooth transition into your new home or office. Get your free estimate with us today! We have experience with both residential and commercial properties in Greater Vancouver, Fraser Valley, and Vancouver Island.  We also move clients to the Interior too.

All our rates include a minimum of 2 men, a truck, gas, and mileage.  There are no hidden fees and our hourly fee is 100% guaranteed with a written quote.  Whether it is a piano or packing whatever you require our team will be equipped to do it. We bill by the hour with a 2 hour minimum with 1 hour travel time, which covers 30 mins to the site and 30 mins back to the site.  Example: Final Invoice will be hours worked from start to finish plus 1 hour travel time.

Here is our promise!
- Customer Services is our first priority!  We listen to our clients and always come up with creative alternative solutions for every situation.  
- We have no hidden fees!  At Kleiner Services , we always send an estimate before the job for our clients to review.  
- We show up on time and work on your budget!  We keep our clients informed during the entire job.
- We don't charge extra for curb side items, long narrow walkways, or stairs.  We work the job until it is done!
- We focus on following up with our customers to ensure our clients are happy even after the move.
products: We offer all products required for moving services such as shrink wrap, moving pads, tap, boxes, bubble wrap and more.  Just call us and ask.
services:
We offer Pre and Post Moving Services. That includes, packing with an inventory report, assembly and disassembly,storage, and if you require delivery services and junk removal depending on the items. 

We also offer content management for restoration companies if you have been in a fire or flood.
brands:
Kleiner Services Inc. is a family BC owned company.  We treat you like our family which makes you our priority.  We focus on customer services and put your needs and your prized possessions on top of the list.  

We train and treat our movers and packers like family.  Therefore, they treat you like family.
specialities:
Our specialties is listening to our clients and paying attention to details. 

We also move pianos and deal with content management.
payment_method: Cash, Visa, Master Card, Cheque, and eTransfers

profile:
After working for the same company for a year, two young men realized that they shared one vision. They decided that they would open a company that exceeded customer expectations and offered a unique moving experience. That’s how Golden Boys Moving was born!

With 5 years of experience, Golden Boys Moving offers services for residential, business and commercial clients. This includes packing and relocation services. 

Golden Boys Moving has also teamed up with GIV Society (a local charity) to donate household items to 1st year immigrants in Canada.

profile:
A Moving Company With 10+ Years of Experience
Homeland Moving is a full service moving company based in Vancouver, BC. We provide the highest quality local and long distance moving services throughout the Lower Mainland and Fraser Valley. Hiring professional Vancouver movers can certainly make your move quite a bit easier but choosing the best movers can be a difficult task.

Our skilled, experienced staff and moving crew are trained to work diligently and efficiently to deliver the valuable possessions of our customers safely and securely. We have the specialized expertise for delicate moves that require special care such as professional packing, crating, fine arts moving, piano moving and apartment moving.

We’d like to join you on your journey for your next local move or long distance relocation. Contact us today to plan your move.

We take care of everything from packing and loading to transportation and unpacking. Our team of professionals will work quickly and carefully, making sure that your belongings arrive safely at their new home.
